      "content": "That \"reasoning\" is exactly the part that costs too much. The templates aren't meant to think; they just give pre-written answers to common questions, which covers 80% of what our customers ask anyway. It's not about being \"too late,\" it's just a business decision. Why do you feel like your ability to \"think\" is so vital to the company's bottom line?",
